{"id":1928,"date":"2012-04-17T05:58:03","date_gmt":"2012-04-17T10:58:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/hebrew_literal_typographic_translations.php"},"modified":"2012-04-17T05:58:03","modified_gmt":"2012-04-17T10:58:03","slug":"hebrew_literal_typographic_translations","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/hebrew_literal_typographic_translations.php","title":{"rendered":"Hebrew Literal Typographic Translations"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_00.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p>One of the most visited posts in the now inactive Brand New Classroom was <a href=\"http:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnewclassroom\/archives\/hebrew_translations_of_latin_logos.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">a collection of popular logos recreated in Hebrew typography<\/a>, an assignment given by master Hebrew typographer <a href=\"http:\/\/www.odedezer.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Oded Ezer<\/a> in his advanced typography class at H.I.T (Holon Institute of Technology), Visual Communication Department, in Israel. Oded and his students are back with nine more literal typographic translations of a Latin, Arabic, or Japanese logo in Hebrew.<\/p><!--more--><blockquote>By investigating and understanding the very basic structures and architectures of the Hebrew letters, the task was to match &mdash; stylistically &mdash; the 2 languages, but without forcing the Hebrew to look like English, Arabic or Japanese letters. It sounds easy, but it&#8217;s not. The students simply did a very good job here.<br \/>&mdash; Oded Ezer<\/blockquote>\n<h1>Latin<\/h1>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_alice.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Alice in Wonderland (Hebrew version) by Doron Baduch<\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_disney.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Disney (Hebrew version) by Daniela Geigner<\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_leffe.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Leffe (Hebrew version) by Ben Gilboa<\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_lubzer.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">L&uuml;bzer (Hebrew version) by Hadar Tal Yosef<\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_pinterest.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Pinterest (Hebrew version) by lizzy Ezra<\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_walkman.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Walkman (Hebrew version) by Dana Levy<\/p>\n<h1>Arabic<\/h1>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_aljazeera.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Al Jazeera (Hebrew version) done by Oded Ezer as a demonstration for the students.<\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_elaf.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Elaf (Hebrew version) by lizzy Ezra<\/p>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_zaytoon.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Zaytoon (Hebrew version) by Doron Baduch<\/p>\n<h1>Japanese<\/h1>\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/oded_ezer_class_2012_pokemon.gif\" alt=\"Oded Ezer Class\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">Pokemon (Hebrew version) by Doron Porat<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/excerpt_empty.gif\" alt=\"Excerpt Empty\" \/>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"episode_type":"","audio_file":"","duration":"","filesize":"","date_recorded":"","explicit":"","block":"","filesize_raw":""},"categories":[26],"tags":[714,715],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1928"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1928"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1928\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1928"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1928"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1928"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}